misc/

# The vendored Sileo tree must keep its shared scheme and SwiftPM pins, which
# the blanket xcshareddata/ rule above would otherwise drop. `make package`
# runs `xcodebuild -scheme Sileo`, so without the scheme the build fails on a
# fresh clone, and without Package.resolved the dependencies are unpinned.
!Sileo/**/xcshareddata/
!Sileo/**/xcshareddata/**
# Build outputs of the vendored tree
Sileo/packages/
Sileo/giveMeRoot/bin/
